      <body>
        <div>
            <pb facs="#TL-0500.jpg" n="part4_p026.jpg" xml:id="img_0026" corresp="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/tillich-lectures/part4_p026.jpg"/>
            
            <p facs="#facs_26_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>-495.
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>QN: My question is this: In your last lecture you distinguished three type of truths, or truth¬
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>on three different levels, such as truth in the realm of subject-object experience, and truth in
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>the realm of good and beautiful, and also existentalist truth. Now you said that these three
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>types or levels of truths are interpenetrate, but they shouldn’t interfere in each other's realm
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>because then eternal conflict results—
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>PT: Yes. Yes.
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>existentalist
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>QN: But I think that if the third type of truth which is
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>truth and claims to be the ultimate
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_11" n="N011"/>truth, I think that it should take into consideration the other type of truths and should bring under
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_12" n="N012"/>judgment,
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_13" n="N013"/>if it is, the UITIMATE truth, as a criterion for the other type of truth. So I think
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_14" n="N014"/>that the third type of truth should interfere in the other realms.
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_1_tl_15" n="N015"/>PT: Yes, now, "correlate" and "interfere" are two very different things. If you say "intrefere," you
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_26_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/>mean that the so-called UITIMATE truth—I would say with about the ultimate, which is a little bit
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>different in meaning—if the existential truth or the truth about our ultimate concern interferes with
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>the first two levels, the experimental and the experiential truth, then you make, in the [name?] of your
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>existental relationship to the ultimate meaning of your life, or the ground of being, or to God (however
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>you want to express it, in this moment), a judgment about the fact whether there was snow in the night
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_6" n="N006"/>or not! Now this cannot be done! — this simply cannot be donel No " photographic" facts can be
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_7" n="N007"/>determined in the name of UITIMATE truth. If this were the case, then the level were not only
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_3_tl_8" n="N008"/>mixed, and there [was] (mutual defensive, but then the ultimate wouldn’t really be ultimate,
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_26_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>because then you could say it is an information about facts—of having snowed or not
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>having
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>snowed, or about the relationship of H2O, the chemical elements in the ocean, which are a matter
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>of experiment and nothing else. And if, in the name of the third level of truth, you make
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>a judgment about the first level (let us stick to the first, for the moment), then you do something
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>souhaitez lʼhonneur dʼautre sérieusement beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>sʼil est en a
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>by the
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>dans le
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_11" n="N011"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_12" n="N012"/>dʼune manière beaucoup de lʼadresse
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_13" n="N013"/>Vous avez
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_14" n="N014"/>des
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_15" n="N015"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_16" n="N016"/>Votre
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_17" n="N017"/>dans cette teinte vieuse,
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_18" n="N018"/>dʼune manière de
               <lb facs="#facs_26_tr_2_tl_19" n="N019"/>dʼun autre vie de ses
            </p>
            
